{"tid":5841,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"簡老公 一定要簡用nokia","createTime":"2016-11-27T05:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T09:14:33.000Z","uid":19502,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef00a8272aa09608962669a800404c877255bb2a","tid":5841,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"好多女人揀男人會睇男方既錢銀多少同地位高低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就話 <br />\n睇男人 要睇手機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢同地位雖然重要 <br />\n但係你睇下依家有幾多有錢佬無人性兼無個性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男人有個性更值得女人去愛 <br />\n<br />\n而Nokia手機係男人個性既體現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黝黑既外殼突出男人既沉穩 <br />\n流線形既設計表現出男人既線條美 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n持久既電池代表男人既活力充沛 <br />\n堅實既質料顯示出男人既安全感 <br />\n<br />\n想像一下 <br />\n當你同班MK仔MK妹係強國地鐵落難 <br />\nMK仔手上面只係一部又一部既iphone同android <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然而你係褲袋掏出左你部手機 <br />\n你用Nokia手機一野就打爆左車窗 <br />\n側邊既MK妹會向你投下感激既眼神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你比返個充滿自信既眼神比佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住你拖住佢地一齊逃出依個即將爆炸既車廂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你騫然發現係車廂之中 <br />\n班MK仔仲攞住生活態度同生活智慧敲個車窗有D機仲爛埋添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你會心微笑 <br />\n然後轉身離開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭先D mk妹早就比你電到暈哂 <br />\n仲唔快搭車去MK開房 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3P4P隨便你 <br />\n記得唔好再搭錯強國車 <br />\n<br />\n所以話沉穩同安全感依D野有錢有地位都買唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而Nokia手機可以助你表現你既獨特個性同埋安全感 <br />\n男人會欣賞你既與眾不同 <br />\n囡囡會鍾意成熟穩重既你 <br />\n所以話睇男人 先要睇手機 <br />\n好男人更加需要Nokia手機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n倘若有人問你 <br />\n乜你仲用Nokia手機既咁鬼out day架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你擰一擰個頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑左一笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48049e6d13b7d9195e3d1529647c9a3e3f26dffe","tid":5841,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"Strong post leave name<br />\n<br />\n利申：用開Nokia 但係上唔到lihkg先轉iphone"},{"pid":"475597b0f67e639a54c8730a1d14228abba93ce0","tid":5841,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Strong post leave name<br />\n<br />\n利申：用開Nokia 但係上唔到lihkg先轉iphone</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4ed89fdd7f17e93b6817ff4b0ac54f7658a6ff","tid":5841,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:53:56.000Z","msg":"新潮文的誕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf750a19be28fa4f81182a942f1e263a30cb3d3","tid":5841,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8b98b81a48215cf361f9b7c2020de5be58cf0a","tid":5841,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351bdc7f71269f9b7700f069fde0ef2dc78b168e","tid":5841,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd11265d5766f451c83c6823047f194cba8def1","tid":5841,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\